  <header class="main-hd">
    <h3 class="title">
      <a href="https://book.douban.com/review/2349343/" class="title-link">自识而已</a>
      <div class="toggle_review right">        <a href="javascript:;" id="toggle-2349343"class="indicator unfold j" title="展开全文">        </a>
      </div>
    </h3>
    

<div class="header-more">
    <a class="author-avatar" href="https://www.douban.com/people/1079758/"><img width="48" height="48" src="https://img1.doubanio.com/icon/u1079758-7.jpg"></a>
    <a href="https://www.douban.com/people/1079758/" class="author">
      <span property="v:reviewer">vir</span>
    </a>    <span property="v:rating" class="allstar40 main-title-rating" title="推荐"></span>
  <span property="v:dtreviewed" content="2009-09-17"
      class="main-meta">2009-09-17 17:15:53</span>
</div>

  </header>

        <div class="main-bd">
          <div id="review_2349343_short" class="review-short">
            <div class="short-content">
                      从其论述Heidegger部分来看，相较于他早年的著作《现象学的效应》，倪老师终于达到了他作为一个现象学者所应有的水平。只是在其运思之中还可以看到其有执于Husserl现象学并不免流露出护教的教条色彩，以致于评述Heidegger有关In-sein的洞识时，仍有一层薄薄的纸片还没捅破...

                    <a class="pl" href="https://book.douban.com/review/2349343/#comments">(7回应)</a>
                  <div class="more-info pl clearfix">
                    <span class="left">5有用 / 0没用</span>
                  </div>
            </div>
          </div>
          <div id="review_2349343_full" class="hidden">
            <div id="review_2349343_full_content" class="full-content"></div>
          </div>
        </div>
    </div>
  </div>





